    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold pb-10 font-sans mx-5 text-center">How Much is Flight Training Going to Cost?</h2>
    <p class="w-3/4 pb-10">The cost of flight training varies greatly depending on a number of factors such as type of training, the student's aptitude and experience level, and the type of aircraft used.</p>
    <p class="w-3/4 pb-10">When first starting out, many people only look at the hourly rate for aircraft rental.  However, take into consideration the program as a whole.  Ideal Aviation has great aircraft availability so you can fly more often and retain your knowledge and skills better so you can pass the checkride in a shorter time.</p>
